    "TITLE": "Welcome to the Future of Construction",
    "SUBTITLE": "Be part of the change. Connect. Transform. Build.",
    "BODY": "The Industrialized Construction Cluster of Catalonia is not just a network of companies: it is the core where those redesigning the sector converge. Being part of the CCIC means entering an active innovation community where experience blends with disruption and real opportunities for collaboration, visibility, and growth emerge.<br><br><b>Here, connections are created with leading companies in the sector along with a diverse range of SMEs and visionary professionals</b>. We are rethinking every construction process for its industrialization, seeking to improve efficiency and sustainability. From new products and modular systems to algorithms that think faster than regulations, the ecosystem moves forward… and you can be part of it.<br><br><i>If you believe that industrialization, data, and applied intelligence can transform the way we build, you are in the right place. If you want to combine capabilities, share projects, or scale your impact, join today.</i><br><br><b>Pre-register, I will contact you and send detailed information on how to access our network.</b>"
  },
